GridCollectionOpt
public abstract class GridSerializableCollection<E>
extends AbstractCollection<E>
implements Serializable

Makes AbstractCollection as Serializable and is useful for making anonymous serializable collections. It has no extra logic or state in addition to AbstractCollection.
